<br>
I've completed it on all but the hardest difficulty setting now but god damn are the returned jedi tough on the hardest setting. <br>
<br>
Multiplayer:<br>
<br>
Not so good imho.  Force powers just make it more annoying(after the 100th time you get pushed over an edge it gets a bit old) and you can't do the funky spinning in midair moves.  The Luke Skywalker bot is an animal, he rips you apart in 1-2 hits.  I thought there were only 1-2 really good multiplayer levels the others were all a bit uninspired.<br>
<br>
Will be nice to see what mods come out for it though and the teamplayer multiplayer has some interesting stats to it.<br>
<br>
<br>
I'll give it an 7/10.<br>
<br>
Great graphics but just too darn short. <p><html>
